description: Exhaustive technical audit ruleset for the Docker base-image monorepo CI/CD pipeline. Apply to ALL files unless scoped otherwise.
globs: ["**/*.groovy", "**/*.py", "**/*.yaml", "**/*.yml", "**/*.j2", "**/Dockerfile*", "**/*.sh", "**/*.conf", "**/*.md"]
